 Village Christian 60, Whitter Christian 49 -- Jeanne Beauchamp and Lindy James 
each scored 15 points to lead the Crusaders (24-1) in a Division IV-A 
quarterfinal game at Sonora High. 
</P>
<P>
 The Crusaders will meet Bell-Jeff in the semifinals on Saturday night. 
</P>
