 Newbury Park 64, St. Lucy's 51 -- Kara McKeown had 13 points, 23 rebounds, six 
steals and five assists to lead the Panthers (23-4) in a Division III-AA 
quarterfinal at Newbury Park. Julie Wastell added 20 points and six steals for 
the winners. 
</P>
<P>
