the City Section 4-A Division playoffs. 
</P>
<P>
 A 10-0 run to start the second half gave the Huskies a 32-22 lead midway 
through the third quarter, but Belmont trimmed its deficit to 34-30 at the end 
of the period. 
</P>
<P>
 Celaya hit one of two free throws to trim North Hollywood's deficit to 44-43 
