<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 24, 1994, Thursday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 8; Column 1; Metro Desk 
</P>
