investigators said. 
</P>
<P>
 Ricky Lawrence La Rue shot Anthony Fuentes, 29, nine times with a 
semiautomatic handgun after an argument in La Rue's front yard involving the 
two men and La Rue's wife, Kimberly, 22.Then La Rue apparently turned the gun 
