Winter Olympics (Fri.) KCBS 28.6 3. Winter Olympics (Sat.) KCBS 24.5 Winter 
Olympics (Thurs.) KCBS 24.5 5. Winter Olympics (Tues.) KCBS 23.0 6. 60 Minutes 
KCBS 21.5 7. Winter Olympics (Wed.) KCBS 20.2 8. Winter Olympics (Mon.) KCBS 
