<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA022494-0371 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 016945 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 24, 1994, Thursday, Valley Edition 
</P>
